// Hub_in_physicallayer_in_computerNetwork ka mtlb ki ComputerNetwork meh physicallayer meh Hub-device
// Hub bhi ek pure hardware device hai.
// simply bas Hub is a multiport-repeater plus additionally apn aseh bol sktehh hai ki Hub multiple-device ka connecting-point hota hai toh mtlb esmeh repeater se thodi jada functionalities hoti hai jaise in form of led-lights ki kon-kon si device connected hai ya konsi meh broken connection hai etc..etc..
// Hub signal-forwarding krta hai
// Hub meh signal-filtering nhi hoti hai.(mtlb Hub pe jis bhi device se data(signal) aaya for the other-device toh Hub toh sare Network k devices meh ess signal ko forward krdeta hai, aur khne ka mtlb broadcast krdeta hai to all the devices in ComputerNetwork.)
// Hub meh collisons hotehh hai, and maximumly hotehh hai mtlb collision minimize krne ki koi facility nhi hoti Hub meh.
// Hub meh signal-traffic high hi rheta hai, mtlb repeater se bhi high rheta hai q ki Network k sabhi devices ka signal phle ess Hub pe hi aayegana isiliy mtlb Hub pe traffic high hi rheta hai.

